\par 
\par \tab 6. Save the texture as a .wal file into your custom .wal directory below ..\\baseq2\\textures\\ and make sure you have set the \plain\f2\fs20\cf1\strike Flags\plain\f2\fs20\cf2 {\v Scribble41}\plain\f2\fs20  for the texture name.
